snippet.title: Untitled Rhythm Puzzle Game - V0.4 Unofficial Trailer
snippet.description:
Untitled Rhythm Puzzle Game is a game in development under the Game Studio Live and Digital Dungeoneers brand. Find out more soon at https://dungeoneers.tv/untitled-rhythm-puzzle-game.

Featured Streamers:

Hellmight: https://www.twitch.tv/hellmight
Losthope_tv: https://www.twitch.tv/losthope_tv
Redman465: https://www.twitch.tv/redman465/

In the big city Blob is a high profile DJ, playing to the biggest crowds. But then one day he didn't look both ways when crossing the road, and has now found himself in Rhythm Purgatory. You must help him get up the stairway to heaven, as you slowly descend into madness... In the first every Untitled Rhythm Puzzle Game (URPG) will you be a winner or a loser in the way of the beat?

This game was first created as a prototype for the Digital Dungeoneers' first ever charity livestream.
